snippet.title: Season 4 Royale Pass - How to Upgrade
snippet.description:
Upgrade your Season 4 Royale Pass to speed up your progress in PUBG Mobile and earn awesome exclusive rewards.

Participate in Daily Missions and Elite Missions to rank up faster.

Tons of new items and rewards in the Season 4 Royale Pass.
